# partition

```
cd partition2
futhark bench --backend=cuda partition2.fut
```

staticWithOpt : scatter static safe, no replicate (eliminated opt)
staticChecked : scatter static safe, but has replicate
staticDynChecked : safe scatter dyn check

# kmeans

Get datasets: https://github.com/diku-dk/futhark-ad/tree/master/kmeans/kmeans-sparse/data

```
cd kmeans-sparse
futhark bench --backend=cuda --tuning=k10-manual.fut k10-manual-dynamic.fut
futhark bench --backend=cuda --tuning=k10-manual.fut k10-manual-static.fut
```

kmeans has to be done manually:
  search for "remove me and you'll see a 2x slowdown"
futhark bench --backend=cuda k10-manual.fut
